ably alright there.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-3-part-1-2023-01-18-10-52-01/43.mp3","time_start":109.89,"time_end":113.81},{"position":44,"content":"I think so, yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-3-part-1-2023-01-18-10-52-01/44.mp3","time_start":113.81,"time_end":115.23},{"position":45,"content":"Do they want any special experience?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-3-part-1-2023-01-18-10-52-01/45.mp3","time_start":115.58,"time_end":118.17},{"position":46,"content":"I think they wanted some experience of teleconferencing.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-3-part-1-2023-01-18-10-52-01/46.mp3","time_start":118.32,"time_end":121.99},{"position":47,"content":"I've got three years' experience of that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-3-part-1-2023-01-18-10-52-01/47.mp3","time_start":122.4,"time_end":124.89},{"position":48,"content":"Let's see, yes, good.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-3-part-1-2023-01-18-10-52-01/48.mp3","time_start":125.51,"time_end":127.67},{"position":49,"content":"In fact they're only asking for at least one year, so that's great.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-3-part-1-2023-01-18-10-52-01/49.mp3","time_start":127.67,"time_end":132.13},{"position":50,"content":"So is that something that might interest you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-3-part-1-2023-01-18-10-52-01/50.mp3","time_start":132.43,"time_end":134.71},{"position":51,"content":"It is, yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-15-test-3-part-1-2023-01-18-10-52-01/51.mp3","time_start":134.71,"time_end":136.